    "abstractNote": "The present paper opens a series of articles that will precede the critical edition of the \u00abChapters on Knowledge\u00bb of Isaac of Nineveh (to be published in \u00abThe Bible and Christian Antiquity. Supplementum\u00bb book series). In these articles, all the existing Russian translations of the \u00abChapters on Knowledge\u00bb will be revised; further, there will be provided a critical edition of the chapters based on all the known manuscripts, as well as historical and philological notes to the text. In the present article, the Syriac text of the chapters 1\u201310 against the Oxford, Bodleian Library, Ms syr. e. 7, as well as the revised version of Sergey Turkin\u2019s Russian translation are provided.",
